OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1773411079
OL,3,CSerial scrap metal thief spared jail
OL,4,Cafter injuring brewery worker in van
OL,5,Cescape
OL,7,FWATCH: CCTV shows the moment staff
OL,8,Fmember David Daniels became injured.
OL,10,FA 35-year-old man from Birmingham has
OL,11,Fbeen sentenced at Oxford Crown Court
OL,12,Ffollowing a year-long crime spree that
OL,13,Fended with a chaotic getaway at a
OL,14,Fhistoric Oxfordshire brewery.
OL,16,FRelu Tanase, of Fentham Road,
OL,17,FErdington, appeared for sentencing on
OL,18,FMarch 11, 2026, after pleading guilty
OL,19,Fto five counts of theft and one count
OL,20,Fof driving a motor vehicle dangerously.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
