PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1773411079
OL,3,CSerial scrap metal thief spared jail
OL,4,Cafter injuring brewery worker in van
OL,5,Cescape
OL,7,FThe court heard how Tanase's spree
OL,8,Fculminated in a confrontation at Hook
OL,9,FNorton Brewery on July 13, 2025.
OL,11,FThe incident occurred on a Sunday
OL,12,Fevening while staff were sitting
OL,13,Foutside the brewery.
OL,15,FJames Clarke, the brewery's Managing
OL,16,FDirector, spotted a white van on his
OL,17,Fphone's CCTV app: "I saw a gentleman
OL,18,Fhelping himself to scrap metal."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1773411079
OL,3,CSerial scrap metal thief spared jail
OL,4,Cafter injuring brewery worker in van
OL,5,Cescape
OL,7,FWhen staff moved to confront the
OL,8,Fdriver and closed the yard's security
OL,9,Fbarrier, the situation turned violent.
OL,11,FAs a colleague attempted to open the
OL,12,Fgate to let the van leave, the vehicle
OL,13,Fsurged forward before the barrier had
OL,14,Ffully cleared its path.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1773411079
OL,3,CSerial scrap metal thief spared jail
OL,4,Cafter injuring brewery worker in van
OL,5,Cescape
OL,7,FThe impact caused the barrier to flex,
OL,8,Fknocking brewer David Daniels to the
OL,9,Fground. Recalling the moment, Mr.
OL,10,FDaniels said: "He, in his eagerness to
OL,11,Fget out, drove into the end of the
OL,12,Fbarrier that I was holding. And then
OL,13,Fthat sent me flying a little bit".
OL,15,FWATCH: Staff member David Daniels
OL,16,Fdescribes how he became hurt.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1773411079
OL,3,CSerial scrap metal thief spared jail
OL,4,Cafter injuring brewery worker in van
OL,5,Cescape
OL,7,FWhile Mr. Daniels initially got up due
OL,8,Fto adrenaline, his injuries -
OL,9,Fincluding a bruised hip and cuts to
OL,10,Fhis arm and ankle - became more
OL,11,Fapparent over the following days.
OL,13,FHe noted that "it could have been a
OL,14,Ffairly substantial injury" had he hit
OL,15,Fthe back of his head on the sloped
OL,16,Fground.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1773411079
OL,3,CSerial scrap metal thief spared jail
OL,4,Cafter injuring brewery worker in van
OL,5,Cescape
OL,7,FThe brewery team was shocked that
OL,8,Fsomeone would be so bold in such a
OL,9,Fquiet village. James Clarke said: "It
OL,10,Fwas just the audacity only to drive by
OL,11,Fand see us here... we don't generally
OL,12,Fget that sort of thing in Hook Norton".
OL,14,FMr. Daniels added: "It's a bit
OL,15,Fworrying, really, that people feel
OL,16,Fthey can come onto sites so brazenly
OL,17,Flike that and just feel they can take
OL,18,Fwhat they want".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
